    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Your hatred of a particular type of creature has honed your killer instinct.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Seething Hatred, sneak attack +3d6, studied target class feature.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>When you succeed at a sneak attack against a creature you selected as the target of your Seething Hatred feat, you use d8s to roll sneak attack damage instead of d6s.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When you succeed at a sneak attack against a creature that is not the target of your Seething Hatred feat, you can spend 5 stamina points to treat the creature as if it were the target of your Seething Hatred for that attack.",
